Ferrovial Wins $60 Million U.K. Rail Contract, Economista Says

-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 
2011-07-16T10:31:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-16/ferrovial-wins-60-million-u-k-rail-contract-economista-says.html
Ferrovial SA (FER) , a Spanish construction
company, won a 37 million-pound ($60 million) signaling contract
from the U.K.’s Network Rail,  El Economista  reported.  Ferrovial will install new signaling systems on lines in
Yorkshire, Nottingham,  London  and Devon, the newspaper said,
citing people at the company it didn’t identify.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Sills in Madrid at   bsills@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Reed Landberg at   landberg@bloomberg.net  